headline.main: Griezmann, Gameiro Get Atletico Back to Winning Ways
headline.print_headline: Griezmann, Gameiro Get Atletico Back to Winning Ways

lead_paragraph: Atletico Madrid's French forwards Antoine Griezmann and Kevin Gameiro fired them to a first win in three league outings as they beat Valencia 3-0 on Sunday to maintain their hold on Spain's fourth Champions League qualifying place.
